HEADWORD: Brand iron
<hw>Brand" i`ron</hw>. <sn>1.</sn> <def>A branding iron.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A trivet to set a pot on.</def>
